#!/usr/bin/env bash
set -euo pipefail

## Upkeeper operator.
##
## Version: v1.0.12
##
## Version policy:
## - Any future behavioral, documentation, default, or portability change to
##   this file must update UPKEEPER_VERSION and this header in the same change.
##
## This is local control-plane glue, not a domain build script. Its job is to
## run one backend Codex task at a time, stop before quota exhaustion makes
## things worse, and preserve enough evidence that the next operator or agent
## can see what happened without replaying the incident.

